Debra Cleaver, Vote.org

<img src="https://blog.ycombinator.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/yc-effect-lei.png" alt="Lei Xu, Emote" width="702" height="516" class="size-full wp-image-1096586" /> 

Lei Xu, Emote

