I am assuming that the monetization strategy is ads or something with a lot of audience and that usage is important. If
that is the case, I would give it 3-6 months iterating to crack the k-factor and then consider moving on.

**We are building facebook messenger chatbots for restaurants for getting new customers and re-engaging existing
