**3. Are there any resources you would recommend to gain deep insights into gamification?**

1.  I don't think gamification builds retention. I think the core of your product needs to be retentive and sticky.
    Facebook does a great job at creating a core loop first and then giving you signals and gamifying it.

2.  I'm not familiar with Google Tez scratch cards, but in a non-game, I think creating a core loop of a behavior that
