bought, not sold‚Äîit‚Äôs very difficult to force an acquisition to happen, and nearly impossible if you haven‚Äôt built
something legitimately valuable (somehow, this fact surprises founders who decide ‚Äòwe‚Äôd like to get acquired‚Äô almost
