1.  A list of the Company‚Äôs stockholders, including issuance dates and original issuance price.
2.  A list of the Company‚Äôs option holders, including grant dates and exercise prices.
3.  Copies of agreements relating to outstanding options, warrants, rights (including conversion or preemptive rights)
