4.  Any documents evidencing registration rights for the Company‚Äôs securities, or evidencing any agreements among the
    Company‚Äôs shareholders or between the Company and its shareholders.
5.  A summary of the vesting schedules of any stock or options subject to vesting, including any vesting acceleration.
