There seem to be many founders who can‚Äôt launch because they don‚Äôt have the strong technical skills to build what they
want to build and don‚Äôt know how to find a technical co-founder. So we wanted to offer some advice.

First, are *you* technical enough? It really depends on what you‚Äôre building. If you‚Äôre developing new cancer drugs, you
better be quite technical with biology. But if you‚Äôre building an iPhone app or website, you probably don‚Äôt have to be
that technical to build the first version.

For example, watch [Avni Patel Thompson‚Äôs
