    become friends with engineers and figure out if you‚Äôre compatible them (same process as above). In fact, you
    shouldn‚Äôt care what your role is; this isn‚Äôt for resume building.

Lastly, when you identify the right person. Instead of pitching them directly your idea. Brainstorm ideas with that
person so it evolves with the both of you. This will be a good start to a hopefully lasting relationship of building
